{"tid":991210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底家居電話係呢個時化嘅存在價值係咩?_?","createTime":"2019-01-22T08:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T08:50:57.000Z","uid":229656,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ef763257982fdc142b24bba3182a239e11f325","tid":991210,"uid":229656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的。<br />\n屋企部電話長期得個擺字，響都唔響下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 久而久之已經唔記得咗屋企電話嘅存在。<br />\n有日老母忽然講咗句：不如取消咗屋企電話去啦<br />\n嗰下一言驚醒洛克人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呢個世代有邊個唔係有最少一部手提電話係手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且依家大部分嘅手提電話plan 都係無限分鐘通話時間；打長途又唔使用到長途電話，一個網絡電話+facetime 就得。<br />\n<br />\n試問又有幾何會用到屋企電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10e6eac5c7db74c34b450a2881c1d33bab56752","tid":991210,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:10:19.000Z","msg":"我都想知時化係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da986c4a6b4eec0c7f47d1570bdba8c62c5fce8","tid":991210,"uid":229656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a10e6eac5c7db74c34b450a2881c1d33bab56752","tid":991210,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:10:19.000Z","msg":"我都想知時化係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"眼殘打錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d476463bd97ec550cf1dbc07f0f508b5b9c99c","tid":991210,"